        public void setProcessCoeffDataDescription(java.lang.String desc)

If the description entered is a PROCESS and is not null it will bring in the string description(trimmed) of the process and use this to set the process coefficient data. It then turns off processCoefficient Data default description, and marks system knowledge changed.
